title: R-Ladies Göttingen Meet-Up 04
description:
Hey everybody!
In our next meetup, Triet Doan will give a talk about reproducible research (and Github). ✨

We have one additional smaller slot, in case anyone else would like to give a short lightning talk. Just fill in the form here, and we'll get back to you: https://r-ladiesgoe-lightningtalks.formr.org/

As always, let us know if there are any questions or suggestions!

We’re looking forward to seeing you!

RLadies Göttingen

title: R-Ladies Göttingen Meet-Up 03
description:
This time, Laura is going to tell us about her experience with creating an R package!

We have an additional one or two slots, in case anyone else would like to present. If so, let us know here - you can also let us know if you would like to present some other time in the future: https://r-ladiesgoe-lightningtalks.formr.org/

Afterwards, we’d like to watch/work through the first half of this introduction to the tidyverse by RLadies Amsterdam, for anyone who’s interested: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aHTCuJiV7EY

As always, let us know if there are any questions or suggestions!

We’re looking forward to seeing you!

RLadies Göttingen
